      <h2>Brand Identity</h2>

      <p>The publication name is always written as <strong>The Freethinking Times</strong> — capitalised, no abbreviation. The icon is a pansy flower, a historical symbol of freethought (from the French <em>pens&eacute;e</em>, meaning "thought").</p>

      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-4);padding:var(--space-6);background:var(--color-bg-alt);border:1px solid var(--color-rule);margin:var(--space-6) 0;">
        <img src="/assets/favicon.svg" alt="Pansy icon" width="48" height="48">
        <span style="font-family:var(--font-masthead);font-size:var(--text-xl);font-weight:700;">{{ site.title }}</span>
      </div>

      <p><strong>Tagline:</strong> {{ site.description }}</p>

      <h2>Typography</h2>

      <p>Four font families, each with a specific role. All loaded from <a href="https://fonts.bunny.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bunny Fonts</a> (privacy-friendly, no tracking).</p>

